HAL library.

To build:
  1) make all

To integrate:
  1) make all
  2) Update your build system with 
       Compilation: HAL := {absolute path to HAL}
                    include ${HAL}/hal.mk
                    g++ ${EXPORT_DIR} yours.cpp ...

       Link:        g++ yours.o ... ${LD_FLAGS} 

For more detailes please see example/main.cpp
